1
00:00:19,360 --> 00:00:20,160
Mother.

2
00:00:21,960 --> 00:00:24,080
I made you a bowl of egg noodles today.

3
00:00:41,560 --> 00:00:42,960
My mother died unjustly.

4
00:00:43,800 --> 00:00:46,040
I will avenge her no matter what.

5
00:00:50,760 --> 00:00:52,720
I will kill Song Huainan.

6
00:01:02,520 --> 00:01:03,200
Qingzhou.

7
00:01:04,879 --> 00:01:05,880
I heard

8
00:01:06,440 --> 00:01:07,360
the Governor is

9
00:01:07,360 --> 00:01:09,200
inspecting the nearby towns.

10
00:01:10,200 --> 00:01:12,920
He might be coming here next.

11
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:13,920
The Governor.

12
00:01:15,280 --> 00:01:16,440
If the Governor finds out

13
00:01:16,440 --> 00:01:18,240
about everything Song Huainan has done,

14
00:01:18,240 --> 00:01:20,500
he'll be stripped of his military power.

15
00:01:21,880 --> 00:01:24,480
Then I can avenge my mother.

16
00:01:24,800 --> 00:01:26,880
Luo Li, I want to go see him.

17
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:14,640
So,

18
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:17,340
he really is making private deals with Johnson.

19
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:19,079
There's so much here.

20
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:21,680
Arms and medicine.

21
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:24,680
What exactly is Song Huainan up to?

22
00:02:49,079 --> 00:02:50,210
It was Song Huainan.

23
00:02:51,040 --> 00:02:53,360
He forced me to do it.

24
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:02,490
Someone, come here!

25
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:03,880
Young Master.

26
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:06,400
Go to the Song family and find Marshal Song.

27
00:03:07,440 --> 00:03:10,440
Tell him I want to discuss the factory with him.

28
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:11,480
Yes, sir.

29
00:03:14,640 --> 00:03:16,560
Song Huainan.

30
00:03:35,480 --> 00:03:36,280
Dr. Chen.

31
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:39,000
I advise you to reconsider.

32
00:03:39,200 --> 00:03:41,730
Is your professional ethics more important,

33
00:03:42,079 --> 00:03:43,240
or your life?

34
00:03:49,320 --> 00:03:50,520
Do you recognize her?

35
00:03:50,680 --> 00:03:52,140
I did the plastic surgery.

36
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:54,600
I performed the surgery myself.

37
00:03:58,680 --> 00:03:59,810
What about this one?

38
00:04:00,640 --> 00:04:01,440
It's her.

39
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:03,160
It's also her.

40
00:04:04,600 --> 00:04:05,640
Yao Shengsheng.

41
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:07,240
Zhu Luoli.

42
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:17,320
Very well.

43
00:04:21,880 --> 00:04:22,680
Very well.

44
00:04:22,960 --> 00:04:23,880
Zhu Luoli.

45
00:04:23,880 --> 00:04:27,410
How dare you disguise yourself as Yao Shengsheng to deceive me!

46
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:33,000
You really have a death wish.

47
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:37,600
Young Master,

48
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:39,800
is the Young Mistress home?

49
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:41,200
The Young Mistress went out and hasn't returned.

50
00:04:41,200 --> 00:04:42,159
Where did she go?

51
00:04:42,159 --> 00:04:43,840
I'm not sure.

52
00:04:45,200 --> 00:04:46,000
Young Master,

53
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:48,280
Master Yao sent a messenger today.

54
00:04:48,280 --> 00:04:49,560
He asks you to visit Yao's Soap

55
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:50,960
to discuss

56
00:04:50,960 --> 00:04:52,490
what to do with the factory.

57
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:58,280
Ye.

58
00:05:01,360 --> 00:05:02,200
Yao Lifu.

59
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:10,080
Song Huainan, you're finally here.

60
00:05:12,040 --> 00:05:13,040
Mr. Johnson.

61
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:14,600
Mr. Johnson.

62
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:17,800
It looks like someone broke into the base.

63
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:18,600
This is bad.

64
00:05:18,640 --> 00:05:19,640
We can't let anyone find out

65
00:05:19,640 --> 00:05:20,960
about the poppies in the base.

66
00:05:20,960 --> 00:05:22,280
Everyone, go search!

67
00:05:22,280 --> 00:05:24,080
Kill any suspicious intruders on sight.

68
00:05:24,080 --> 00:05:24,880
Yes, sir.

69
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:47,960
Where is Yao Shengsheng?

70
00:05:49,760 --> 00:05:52,880
Wasn't forcing my father to death enough?

71
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:56,080
Must you wipe out the entire Yao family?

72
00:05:58,720 --> 00:06:00,200
You're just an actor.

73
00:06:00,760 --> 00:06:02,680
How dare you point a gun at me?

74
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:04,440
Put the gun down.

75
00:06:05,200 --> 00:06:06,120
Song Huainan.

76
00:06:07,960 --> 00:06:10,240
I'm asking you one last time.

77
00:06:11,080 --> 00:06:11,920
Do you...

78
00:06:13,320 --> 00:06:15,840
...really have no affection for me?

79
00:06:18,280 --> 00:06:19,940
If it weren't for old times...

80
00:06:19,960 --> 00:06:22,560
Do you think I would have let you live this long?

81
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:36,840
Should I be grateful to you, then?

82
00:06:38,080 --> 00:06:40,520
Thanks for sparing my life.

83
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:44,200
I thought

84
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:47,840
you wouldn't be this heartless.

85
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:52,200
I didn't expect

86
00:06:53,960 --> 00:06:55,880
that nothing matters to you.

87
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:00,880
I hate...

88
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:05,840
I hate myself for not seeing through you sooner.

89
00:07:07,280 --> 00:07:09,120
I hate how I treated Zhu Luoli...

90
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:11,400
After doing such a thing.

91
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:17,720
Do you have to be so ruthless?

92
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:29,360
Yao Lifu.

93
00:07:31,280 --> 00:07:33,840
Yao Shengsheng is Zhu Luoli in disguise.

94
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:38,720
She's back for revenge.

95
00:07:48,200 --> 00:07:50,730
It doesn't matter. I'll give you another one.

96
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:58,360
No wonder.

97
00:08:01,520 --> 00:08:03,200
The bracelet I gave her,

98
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:07,000
she didn't notice anything different.

99
00:08:14,320 --> 00:08:15,320
So what?

100
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:19,120
Even if Zhu Luoli is back for revenge,

101
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:20,600
It was you.

102
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:24,120
You killed the entire Zhu family.

103
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:26,360
You are the executioner.

104
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:30,320
Do you think the Yao family

105
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:32,120
had nothing to do with it?

106
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:41,080
We destroyed the Zhu family together back then.

107
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:43,720
They promised the secret recipe would be mine.

108
00:08:54,880 --> 00:08:56,940
The Yao family was an accomplice too.

109
00:08:59,880 --> 00:09:00,680
Retribution.

110
00:09:08,320 --> 00:09:09,840
Yao Lifu, are you crazy?

111
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:15,840
Yes, I am.

112
00:09:17,400 --> 00:09:18,600
I am crazy,

113
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:23,040
but I still don't dare to shoot you.

114
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:25,610
I don't have time to play with you here.

115
00:09:34,160 --> 00:09:36,400
I've already shown the Yao family enough respect.

116
00:09:36,400 --> 00:09:38,440
Aren't you all alive and well?

117
00:09:38,760 --> 00:09:42,520
You'd better think about the Zhu family's fate.

118
00:09:43,160 --> 00:09:44,680
I am Song Huainan.

119
00:09:44,920 --> 00:09:47,380
Why would I associate with an actor like you?

120
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:53,040
I'm a coward.

121
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:19,480
Zhu Luoli.

122
00:10:22,160 --> 00:10:23,600
Fine.

123
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:25,480
Fine.

124
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:30,160
I received the great gift

125
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:33,840
you sent me.
